Title: The new colonization of Portugal
DateModified: '2019-02-01'
DatePublished: '2019-02-01'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-new-colonization-of-portugal
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Carlos Vinicius Alencar Borba
AuthorCountry: Brazil
Text: My story will be based on the international connections Portugal has, especially
  from the country it colonized. The influence it has received culturally, in gastronomy
  and other areas. It also will show the perspective of refugees living in the country.
